             was indicted for <rs id="t18061203-52-off303" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-off303" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-off303" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of <rs id="t18061203-52-viclabel304" type="occupation">sir</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18061203-52-victim538 t18061203-52-viclabel304"></join> 
                  
                     
                        <persName id="t18061203-52-victim538" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Dunkin
                        <interp inst="t18061203-52-victim538" type="surname" value="Dunkin"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18061203-52-victim538" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18061203-52-victim538" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , about the hour of eight at night, on the <rs id="t18061203-52-cd305" type="crimeDate">28th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18061203-52-off303 t18061203-52-cd305"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18061203-52-off307 t18061203-52-cd305"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18061203-52-off311 t18061203-52-cd305"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18061203-52-off312 t18061203-52-cd305"></join>, with intent to steal, and feloniously stealing therein three feather beds, value 20 l. three counterpanes, value 2 l. two four-post bed furnitures, value 2 l. 2 s. two looking glasses, value 8 l. one pier glass, value 3 l. two candlesticks, value 1 l. the property of sir 
                     <persName id="t18061203-52-person539">
                        William 
                        Dunkin
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-person539" type="surname" value="Dunkin"></interp>
