                  </persName>
             stood <rs id="t18061203-52-off311" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-off311" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-off311" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               indicted again
            </rs> of a <rs id="t18061203-52-off312" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-off312" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-off312" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               similar charge
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Mr. Alley, counsel for the prosecution, declining to offer any evidence, they were both</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18061203-52-verdict313" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18061203-52-verdict313" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
